<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>دُرَّتِي<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>خُضْتُ الْبِحَارَ وَغُصْتُ فِي أَعْمَاقِهَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فَلَعَلَّ فِي الأَعْمَاقِ أَلْقَى دُرَّتِي<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>فَأَغُوصُ مِنْ عُمْقٍ لأَعْمَقَ عَلَّنِي<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أَجِدُ اللآلِئَ كَي أَفُوزَ بِبُغْيَتِي<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>هِيَ دُرَّةٌ أَوْصَافُهَا فَوْقَ الدُّرَرْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>يَهْفُو إِلَيْهَا الأَتْقِيَاءُ مِنَ الْبَشَرْ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>وَمُنَى الأَعَادِي أَنْ تَغُورَ فَلا تُرَى تَحْتَ النَّظَرْ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَإِذَا بَدَتْ يَاسَى الأَعَادِي أَنْ بَدَا فِي أُمَّتِي<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَسْطَ الظَّلامِ الدَّامِسِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>هَذَا الْقَمَرْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>* * *<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>